description:
Colin Browen is the host and lead investigator of Teen Spirit a new series made available thru Verizon Wireless/Complex News. Today Colin shares his experiences growing up in a terrifyingly active haunted house, his investigations into his own high school that astounded everyone and the journey into the paranormal.

PLUS an all new Theater of the Mind!
